/-- A random variable `X` has uniform distribution on `s` if its push-forward measure is
`(Œº s)‚Åª¬π ‚Ä¢ Œº.restrict s`. -/
def IsUniform (X : Œ© ‚Üí E) (support : Set E) (‚Ñô : Measure Œ©) (Œº : Measure E := by volume_tac) :=
  map X ‚Ñô = (Œº support)‚Åª¬π ‚Ä¢ Œº.restrict support
